{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_09_02",
  "title": "伊吹渚 2話 せっかくのライブなのに",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "明日は地方の音楽フェスに出演して\n明後日が新曲のMV撮影……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tomorrow‚ we’re performing at a regional music festival‚\nand the day after that‚ we're filming the music video for our new song…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "それで、琴乃ちゃんだけこれから現地に向かって\nフェス紹介の生放送特番に出演、ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ Kotono-chan is heading to the venue alone now\nto appear on the live special program introducing the festival‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.6666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.8666668256
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃のスケジュールまで把握してるのはさすがだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You even know Kotono's schedule? You really are amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8666668256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても……相当忙しいのに\n地方のフェス出演に五人とも乗り気なのは驚いたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That said… I'm surprised that all five of you\nare so enthusiastic about performing at the regional festival despite being so busy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.9333324432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.9333323479
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "少しでも沢山の人に私達の歌を届けたいですから\nこれくらい平気ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We want to deliver our songs to as many people as possible‚\nso this is nothing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.5333324432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.7666650455
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "少しでも沢山の人に……か。琴乃も\n同じようなことを言ってたよ。二人とも頼もしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To as many people as possible… Kotono\nsaid something similar. You're both reliable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そ、そうなんですか？\nえへへ……ちょっと照れちゃいますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ i-is that so?\nEhehe… That makes me a little embarrassed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.0999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.3666651408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "こほん。えぇっと……私達四人は\n明日の朝に新幹線で向かうんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahem. Well then… the four of us\nare scheduled to take the bullet train there tomorrow morning‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。慌ただしくなってすまないが\n現地で合流しよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. Sorry it's so hectic‚\nbut let's meet up there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.8999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.6333352726
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。沙季ちゃんが当日の予定を\n組んでくれてるので、大丈夫だと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright. Saki-chan has made the schedule\nfor the day‚ so I think it'll be alright.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.6666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.1333312035
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、フェスか～。出番が終わったら\n会場をゆっくり回ってみたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ it's a festival~ After our performance‚\nI'd like to take my time and walk around the venue.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.7666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.7333286604
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで出店にも行ってみたいな～\n有名なご当地グルメも出てるらしいですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to go to the food stalls with everyone‚ you know~\nI heard they're also serving famous local delicacies!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.499995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "あとは、今晩の琴乃ちゃんの生放送出演を\n絶対チェックしないとですね！　録画もしなきゃ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ I have to make sure to check out\nKotono's live broadcast tonight! I have to record it too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.5666625977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "本当にブレないな、渚は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You really never change‚ Nagisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.3999953271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.6666619938
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ、大事に思ってるって言ったじゃないですか\n私は琴乃ちゃんのファン第一号ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told you that she’s really important to me‚ didn't I?\nBecause I'm Kotono's first fan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.8333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.6333342553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "特番のナビゲーター役として頑張る琴乃ちゃんの姿……\nすっごく楽しみなんですよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seeing Kotono-chan doing her best as the navigator for the special program…\nI'm so looking forward to it~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.0666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。それじゃあ俺は琴乃と先に向かうよ\n今日の仕事も頑張ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. Well then‚ I'll head there first with Kotono.\nGood luck with your work today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.0999963444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "はい、行ってらっしゃい！\n明日は楽しみましょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ see you later!\nI'm looking forward to tomorrow!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――音楽フェス当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Music Festival Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.433329773,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1133.3384196000084,
          "startTime": 123.5666681926
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 123.5000015259
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 123.5000015259
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 123.5666681926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "まずいな、月ストのステージの直前だっていうのに\n雨足がだいぶ強くなってきた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is bad… It's just before Moon Tempest's performance‚ but\nthe rain's getting pretty heavy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 131.4333389282
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、もうステージまで十五分しかないのに\nまだ渚達四人が会場に着いてないだなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's worse‚ there's only fifteen minutes left until the stage‚\nand Nagisa's group still hasn't arrived at the venue……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.1666722615,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4120.785395399991,
          "startTime": 139.2874576569
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7066.662597700002,
          "startTime": 142.2333348592
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9099.995931100011,
          "startTime": 144.2666681926
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 141.7666721662
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……ん？　渚から電話だ！\nもしもし、今どこにいるんだ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Hm? It's a call from Nagisa!\nHello‚ where are you now?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.5666722615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.7333358764
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.7333358764
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、すみません！\n今、最寄り駅の、駅ビルにいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ I'm sorry!\nRight now‚ I'm at the nearest station's building.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.7666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.2666599592
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "大雨で新幹線が大幅に遅れてしまって\nさっき着いたところなんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The bullet train was greatly delayed due to the heavy rain‚\nand we just got here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.4666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.8000054996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "しかも冠水してるみたいで、その影響で渋滞が酷くて\nタクシーも遅れてて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Additionally‚ there's flooding‚ so the traffic jams are terrible\nand the taxis are also delayed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.6666803996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "会場に着いたら急いで準備しますけど……\n月ストの出番には間に合わないかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once we arrive at the venue‚ we'll hurry and get ready‚ but…\nwe might not make it in time for Moon Tempest's performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.7333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 175.5666742008
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくのライブなのに……ごめんなさい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although it's a live show… I'm sorry……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.5666742008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.133342902
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "渚達は悪くないよ。ちょっとどうするか考えるから……\nえ？　琴乃？　任せるって……どういうことだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This isn't your fault‚ Nagisa. Just give me a moment to think about what to do…\nEh? Kotono? What do you mean… Leave it to you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.0000035604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono……?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.5333469709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 192.400007534
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "いや、さすがにそんな無理はさせられない\n運営と交渉してみるから少し待ってくれないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I can't make you do something that difficult.\nI'll try to negotiate with the management‚ so could you wait a little?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.6666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……そこまで言うなら……分かった、琴乃に任せるよ\n渚。今、琴乃から提案があったんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you put it that way… Alright‚ I'll leave it to you‚ Kotono.\nNagisa. Just now‚ I got a proposal from Kotono--",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.3333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 209.9000217754
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "提案……？\n琴乃ちゃんはなんて言ってるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A proposal…?\nWhat is Kotono-chan saying?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.8666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "渚達四人が到着するまで、琴乃が一人でステージに\n上がって繋いでくれることになった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Until you four arrive‚ Kotono said she'll go on stage\nand hold down the fort.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.5333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 220.7333591777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？　こんな土砂降りの中ですか！？\nそんな無理しなくても……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eeeh!? In this downpour!?\nShe doesn't have to push herself that hard…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.2999933879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 226.66665802
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、今の琴乃ちゃんなら\nただ無理をしてるっていう訳ではないですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……But‚ if it's the Kotono-chan we know now‚\nshe wouldn't just be pushing herself‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.9999954223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 237.4000278788
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "俺もそう思うよ。ステージを成功させるための\n前向きな覚悟が見えたから、俺も了承したんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think so too. I also approved because I saw\nher positive determination to make the stage a success.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.9999954223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 244.8333662984
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs022.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんをずっと見て来た\n{user}さんがそう言うなら安心ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If {user}-san‚ who's been watching Kotono-chan\nthis whole time‚ says that‚ I feel relieved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.3999954223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs023.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました。琴乃ちゃんに任せます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Alright. I'll leave it to Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 250.2333561258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 253.6666965799
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs024.m4a",
      "text": "「でも、本当に無理はしないでね」って\n伝えておいてもらえますか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could you tell her‚ \"But really‚\ndon't push yourself too hard.\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 256.366662089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs025.m4a",
      "text": "私達も出来る限り急ぎますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll hurry as much as we can.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.8666965799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、伝えておくよ。また何かあればすぐに\n連絡してくれ。気を付けてな、それじゃあまた後で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ I'll tell her. Contact me right away\nif anything happens. Be careful‚ see you later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 265.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 269.5666965799
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs026.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ありがとうございます\nそれでは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ thank you very much.\nBye.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 271.666662089,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}